.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, poker, monopoly
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, puzzles, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, electrician, musician, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rowing, tennis
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the dancer##6
 2. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person playing monopoly is the musician##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is between the dancer and the electrician##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the software-developer##1
10. the electrician is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
12. the dancer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Game    | poker    | mah-jongg             | chess   | monopoly     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles            | reading | chess    |
| Job     | electrician | software-developer | dancer  | musician |
| Sport   | basketball  | golf               | rowing  | tennis   |

