.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, cooking, fishing, sudoku
There 4 different types of food: mango, tomato, kale, cabbage
There are 4 different nationalities: british, malaysian, polish, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person eating mango is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 2. the russian is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 5. the person eating mango is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person eating mango##8
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 8. the malaysian is the person eating tomato##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
10. the person eating kale is not to the left of the person eating mango##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person eating tomato##2
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person eating tomato##8
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
