 7. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 8. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is volleyball##7
 9. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
10. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8
11. the electrician is on the far left##1
12. the videographer is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is skiing##1
14. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
15. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
16. the librarian is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8

